intro: Embark on a nostalgic action-adventure starring a heroic dog
description:
Milo is a very brave, smart, and playful dog! Only he can defeat the cruel King Big Flea and his evil henchmen who are terrorizing the fairy kingdom.

Explore four magical branching locations, solve challenging puzzles, defeat dangerous enemies, and collect dog bones to earn special new abilities.

Playing solo or together with local co-op multiplayer, only you can help Milo in his all-important quest!


Features:
* 2D action adventure gameplay
* Colorful pixelated 8-bit style graphics
* Cute chiptune style music
* Upgrade gear and level up
* Single player or 2 player co-op
